  "body": "We concatenate our messages and then verify them, which is unfortunately wrong, as this is now treated as a single message instead of separate and distinct messages. \r\nWhat we have is \r\n```go\r\n[ ] msgs\r\n```\r\ninstead what we should have is \r\n```go\r\n[ ][ ]msgs\r\n```\r\nThis is being worked on over here https://github.com/phoreproject/bls/pull/13, once that has been merged in we can change our bls API, to take in the newly added verification method.\r\n",
